      "role": "user",
      "content": "That looks pretty good, thanks. Could you actually make it a little more personalized though? Maybe add a line or two about how much we enjoyed the technical deep dive he did during the interview? I want him to feel like we actually paid attention to his work, even if it didn't work out this time.",
