      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Here's a revised draft:\n\nDear Marcus,\n\nI wanted to personally reach out to you regarding the Senior Developer position at our Austin office. We were impressed by your exceptional technical skills and the enthusiasm you brought to the final interview. Your in-depth discussion of our cloud architecture during the technical deep dive session was particularly noteworthy - your ability to break down complex concepts and provide practical examples was a testament to your expertise and passion for software development.\n\nHowever, after careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with another candidate whose experience aligns more closely with our specific cloud architecture needs. Please know that this decision was not made lightly, and we recognize the value you would bring to our team. Your passion for software development and commitment to excellence are truly admirable, and we appreciate the time you invested in our hiring process.\n\nWe wish you the best of luck in your future endeavors and hope that our paths will cross again soon. Your skills and experience would be a great fit for many organizations, and we're confident you'll find a team that values your talents as much as we do.\n\nThank you for your interest in our company, and we wish you continued success in your career.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]\n\nI hope this revised draft captures the personalized touch you",
